Instructions :

1. After Cloning the repositary 
	1. GO to Server folder and use "npm instll" to download all the dependencies
	2. Create a database name called "user" in your local MongoDB And insert a record with desired email and password
	3. Replace the relavent port no in app.js line no 31
	4. run "nodemon server.js". Your server is Live now
	5. Go to Client folder and use "npm install" to download all the dependencies.
	6. Use npm start to run the server .
	7. In the login page use the email and password which you given when creating record . 